data.description: Looking for a beautiful home in the heart of Virginia Beach that is priced to sell? Look no further. This one-level home features a bright and open living room with cathedral ceilings and a gas fireplace. Situated in the Glenwood community, you will enjoy access to community pools, parks, and playgrounds. Within driving distance of beaches, shopping, bases, and the interstate. Come see your new home today!
